GROUND RULES
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

- ALL work happens inside ~/Japan-hack only. Never touch any other directory.
- Create ~/Japan-hack now if it does not exist.
- Run: cd ~/Japan-hack before every single command. Never assume you are 
  already in the right directory.
- If any step fails: stop immediately, print the exact error, and wait.
