═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════

cd ~/Japan-hack

STEP 2A — context-mode
Run:
npm install -g context-mode
context-mode --version
Expected: version string responds

STEP 2B — RTK
Run:
brew install rtk-ai/rtk/rtk
rtk --version
If brew fails, fallback:
  curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rtk-ai/rtk/main/install.sh | bash
  rtk --version
Expected: rtk x.x.x

IMPORTANT: Do NOT run rtk gain yet. 
Do NOT let RTK patch any settings.json automatically if prompted — skip that.

STEP 2C — npx availability check (for Fallow + claude-mem)
Run:
npx --version
Expected: version string (comes with npm, no install needed)

